item.title: CVE-2024-23616|2024-01-25T23:32:25.827Z -- symantec -- server%20management%20suite
item.description: A buffer overflow vulnerability exists in Symantec Server Management Suite version 7.9 and before. A remote, anonymous attacker can exploit this vulnerability to achieve remote code execution as SYSTEM.
